{"tid":1995841,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一見到個\"減價\"牌，D 囡囡就會跳晒掣","createTime":"2020-04-30T14:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T09:12:44.000Z","uid":22927,"like":64,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2afcc52587073170b691ac1449fdea486bb3639c","tid":1995841,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:19:05.000Z","msg":"Hi，又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n明明個減價牌都未試過除落嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解D 囡囡都會覺得真係好鬼抵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你覺得抵唔緊要呀，點解要我企係度等你咁耐呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第八條片就講下我囡囡法拉平時衝入鋪頭睇嘢嘅現像<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以click 入去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以的話就話比小弟知有乜可以改善下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家睇得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HEF15oVgEsQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHEF15oVgEsQ&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=c7819c0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HEF15oVgEsQ</a>"},{"pid":"a49d394149e977e3b05ed51c1bb8b464f7989378","tid":1995841,"uid":22927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開陣台先"},{"pid":"4078e3e40cce711443e51a676072f645a40a11d9","tid":1995841,"uid":12628,"like":23,"dislike":14,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"女人=岸鳩"},{"pid":"415ba0bf8ce4eea515af064f331d98d44b184fa0","tid":1995841,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4078e3e40cce711443e51a676072f645a40a11d9","ti